%%sql
CREATE OR REPLACE TEMP VIEW
sstconsignment 
AS
SELECT 

    c.id as lms_consignment_id
    ,c.cref as lms_consignment_cref
    ,c.cdate as lms_consignment_cdate
    ,c.userid as lms_consignment_userid
    ,c.appointment as lms_consignment_appointment
    ,c.deliverby as lms_consignment_deliverby
    ,c.dconfirmed as lms_consignment_dconfirmed
    ,c.dcomment as lms_consignment_dcomment
    ,c.drefno as lms_consignment_drefno
    ,c.loadid as lms_consignment_loadid
    ,c.delivercustid as lms_consignment_delivercustid
    ,c.mrpcflag as lms_consignment_mrpcflag
    ,c.mrpflag as lms_consignment_mrpflag
    ,c.billcust as lms_consignment_billcust
    ,c.cserviceid as lms_consignment_cserviceid
    ,c.lastupdate as lms_consignment_lastupdate
    ,c.billflag as lms_consignment_billflag
    ,c.missingflag as lms_consignment_missingflag
    ,c.routerateid as lms_consignment_routerateid
    ,c.delivertypeid as lms_consignment_delivertypeid
    ,c.billtypeid as lms_consignment_billtypeid
    ,c.totothersurcharges as lms_consignment_totothersurcharges
    ,c.lhaddrate as lms_consignment_lhaddrate
    ,c.lhcharge as lms_consignment_lhcharge
    ,c.sapbillperiodid as lms_consignment_sapbillperiodid
    ,c.lhrouterateid as lms_consignment_lhrouterateid
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_consignid as lms_parcelbyconsignment_consignid
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggweight as lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggweight
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggchargeweight as lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggchargeweight
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggvolweight as lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggvolweight
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggvolumiserweight as lms_parcelbyconsignment_aggvolumiserweight
    ,pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_noparcels as lms_parcelbyconsignment_noparcels
    ,bcr.id as lms_bill_consignmentr_id
    ,bcr.consignid as lms_bill_consignmentr_consignid
    ,bcr.updatedate as lms_bill_consignmentr_updatedate
    ,bcr.pickuprouteid as lms_bill_consignmentr_pickuprouteid
    ,bcr.deliverrouteid as lms_bill_consignmentr_deliverrouteid
    ,bcr.chargeweight as lms_bill_consignmentr_chargeweight
    ,bcr.noofparcels as lms_bill_consignmentr_noofparcels
    ,bcr.tripdistance as lms_bill_consignmentr_tripdistance
    ,bcr.consignmentvalue as lms_bill_consignmentr_consignmentvalue
    ,bcr.billcust as lms_bill_consignmentr_billcust
    ,bcr.redflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_redflag
    ,bcr.updind as lms_bill_consignmentr_updind
    ,bcr.servicetypeid as lms_bill_consignmentr_servicetypeid
    ,bcr.routemissingind as lms_bill_consignmentr_routemissingind
    ,bcr.chargescalcind as lms_bill_consignmentr_chargescalcind
    ,bcr.cdate1 as lms_bill_consignmentr_cdate1
    ,bcr.invalidpcode as lms_bill_consignmentr_invalidpcode
    ,bcr.programno as lms_bill_consignmentr_programno
    ,bcr.totrate as lms_bill_consignmentr_totrate
    ,bcr.routecharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_routecharge
    ,bcr.minweight as lms_bill_consignmentr_minweight
    ,bcr.minrate as lms_bill_consignmentr_minrate
    ,bcr.corderno as lms_bill_consignmentr_corderno
    ,bcr.custref as lms_bill_consignmentr_custref
    ,bcr.manualupdateflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_manualupdateflag
    ,bcr.prevbillcustid as lms_bill_consignmentr_prevbillcustid
    ,bcr.specdelvehicleid as lms_bill_consignmentr_specdelvehicleid
    ,bcr.specdelmissingrouteflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_specdelmissingrouteflag
    ,bcr.overborderflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_overborderflag
    ,bcr.samedeliverid as lms_bill_consignmentr_samedeliverid
    ,bcr.combineroutecharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_combineroutecharge
    ,bcr.waybillid as lms_bill_consignmentr_waybillid
    ,bcr.routelinecount as lms_bill_consignmentr_routelinecount
    ,bcr.samedelcount as lms_bill_consignmentr_samedelcount
    ,bcr.aweight as lms_bill_consignmentr_aweight
    ,bcr.vweight as lms_bill_consignmentr_vweight
    ,bcr.custref3 as lms_bill_consignmentr_custref3
    ,bcr.units as lms_bill_consignmentr_units
    ,bcr.totsurcharges as lms_bill_consignmentr_totsurcharges
    ,bcr.noofpallets as lms_bill_consignmentr_noofpallets
    ,bcr.invalidpudel as lms_bill_consignmentr_invalidpudel
    ,bcr.sharikaflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_sharikaflag
    ,bcr.sapid as lms_bill_consignmentr_sapid
    ,bcr.totfuelsurcharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_totfuelsurcharge
    ,bcr.totdocsurcharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_totdocsurcharge
    ,bcr.totothersurcharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_totothersurcharge
    ,bcr.specdel as lms_bill_consignmentr_specdel
    ,bcr.quoteflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_quoteflag
    ,bcr.billperiod as lms_bill_consignmentr_billperiod
    ,bcr.billweekr as lms_bill_consignmentr_billweekr
    ,bcr.billperiodflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_billperiodflag
    ,bcr.surhargeflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_surhargeflag
    ,bcr.recalcflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_recalcflag
    ,bcr.quotemissingflag as lms_bill_consignmentr_quotemissingflag
    ,bcr.delivertypeid as lms_bill_consignmentr_delivertypeid
    ,bcr.totcovidsurcharge as lms_bill_consignmentr_totcovidsurcharge
    ,u.id as lms_users_id
    ,u.fullname as lms_users_fullname
    ,u.site as lms_users_site
    ,bc.id as lms_bcustomer_id
    ,bc.name as lms_bcustomer_name
    ,dc.id as lms_dcustomer_id
    ,dc.name as lms_dcustomer_name
    ,brr.id as lms_bill_routerate_id
    ,brr.billcustid as lms_bill_routerate_billcustid
    ,brr.effectivedate as lms_bill_routerate_effectivedate
    ,brr.uomid as lms_bill_routerate_uomid
    ,brr.routetypeid as lms_bill_routerate_routetypeid
    ,brr.servicetypeid as lms_bill_routerate_servicetypeid
    ,brr.minkg as lms_bill_routerate_minkg
    ,brr.minrate as lms_bill_routerate_minrate
    ,brr.addrate as lms_bill_routerate_addrate
    ,brr.servicedays as lms_bill_routerate_servicedays
    ,brr.servicehours as lms_bill_routerate_servicehours
    ,brr.ratecardind as lms_bill_routerate_ratecardind
    ,brr.pickupid as lms_bill_routerate_pickupid
    ,brr.deliverid as lms_bill_routerate_deliverid
    ,brr.description as lms_bill_routerate_description
    ,brr.activeflag as lms_bill_routerate_activeflag
    ,brr.billroutetypeflag as lms_bill_routerate_billroutetypeflag
    ,brr.samedayflag as lms_bill_routerate_samedayflag
    ,brr.specialrateflag as lms_bill_routerate_specialrateflag
    ,brr.tocustid as lms_bill_routerate_tocustid
    ,brr.maxparcel as lms_bill_routerate_maxparcel
    ,brr.returnflag as lms_bill_routerate_returnflag
    ,brr.cutoff as lms_bill_routerate_cutoff
    ,brr.rateperkg as lms_bill_routerate_rateperkg
    ,brr.userid as lms_bill_routerate_userid
    ,brr.authorizeperson as lms_bill_routerate_authorizeperson
    ,brr.updatedate as lms_bill_routerate_updatedate
    ,brr.delivertypeid as lms_bill_routerate_delivertypeid
    ,brr.billyear as lms_bill_routerate_billyear
    ,brr.ecommzoneid as lms_bill_routerate_ecommzoneid
    ,brr.billareaid as lms_bill_routerate_billareaid
    ,brr.routerateoverideflag as lms_bill_routerate_routerateoverideflag
    ,bbt.id as lms_bill_billtypesr_id
    ,bbt.description as lms_bill_billtypesr_description
    ,bbt.surchargeflag as lms_bill_billtypesr_surchargeflag
    ,bzrp.id as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupid
    ,bzrp.description as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupdescription
    ,bzrp.zoneid as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupzoneid
    ,bzrp.zrscode as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupzrscode
    ,bzrp.zonerouteorder as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupzonerouteorder
    ,bzrp.zonetype as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupzonetype
    ,bzrp.broutemasterid as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupbroutemasterid
    ,bzrp.broutecode as lms_bill_zoneroute_pickupbroutecode
    ,bzrd.id as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverid
    ,bzrd.description as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverdescription
    ,bzrd.zoneid as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverzoneid
    ,bzrd.zrscode as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverzrscode
    ,bzrd.zonerouteorder as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverzonerouteorder
    ,bzrd.zonetype as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverzonetype
    ,bzrd.broutemasterid as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverbroutemasterid
    ,bzrd.broutecode as lms_bill_zoneroute_deliverbroutecode
    ,bst.id as lms_bill_servicetype_id
    ,bst.description as lms_bill_servicetype_description
    ,bst.code as lms_bill_servicetype_code
    ,bst.ccode as lms_bill_servicetype_ccode
    ,bzp.id as lms_bill_zone_pickupid
    ,bzp.description as lms_bill_zone_pickupdescription
    ,bzp.zonemasterid as lms_bill_zone_pickupzonemasterid
    ,bzp.countryid as lms_bill_zone_pickupcountryid
    ,bzd.id as lms_bill_zone_deliverid
    ,bzd.description as lms_bill_zone_deliverdescription
    ,bzd.zonemasterid as lms_bill_zone_deliverzonemasterid
    ,bzd.countryid as lms_bill_zone_delivercountryid
    ,bdt.id as lms_bill_delivertype_id
    ,bdt.description as lms_bill_delivertype_description
    ,brmp.id as lms_broutemaster_pickupid
    ,brmp.description as lms_broutemaster_pickupdescription
    ,brmp.code as lms_broutemaster_pickupcode
    ,brmp.brouteparentid as lms_broutemaster_pickupbrouteparentid
    ,brmd.id as lms_broutemaster_deliverid
    ,brmd.description as lms_broutemaster_deliverdescription
    ,brmd.code as lms_broutemaster_delivercode
    ,brmd.brouteparentid as lms_broutemaster_deliverbrouteparentid

FROM dboconsignment c

LEFT JOIN sstparcelbyconsignment pbc on pbc.lms_parcelbyconsignment_consignid = c.id
LEFT JOIN dbobill_consignmentr bcr on bcr.consignid = c.id
LEFT JOIN dbousers u on u.id = c.userid
LEFT JOIN dbocustomer bc on bc.id = bcr.billcust
LEFT JOIN dbocustomer dc on dc.id = c.delivercustid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_routerate brr on brr.id = c.routerateid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_billtypesr bbt on bbt.id = c.billtypeid 
LEFT JOIN dbobill_delivertype bdt on bdt.id = c.delivertypeid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_servicetype bst on bst.id = bcr.servicetypeid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_zoneroute bzrp on bzrp.id = bcr.pickuprouteid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_zoneroute bzrd on bzrd.id = bcr.deliverrouteid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_zone bzp on bzp.id = bzrp.zoneid
LEFT JOIN dbobill_zone bzd on bzd.id = bzrd.zoneid
LEFT JOIN dboBroutemaster brmp on brmp.id = bzrp.broutemasterid
LEFT JOIN dboBroutemaster brmd on brmd.id = bzrd.broutemasterid
